name: X-Ray Heads
description:
This LoRA was created to produce images of complex x-rayed heads filled with mechanical parts. It's triggered with the token "xryhd" and works best with high weight. All of the training images were in profile, so this LoRA will struggle to make images outside of that composition.

Support me on Patreon to get access to all of my latest stuff, or check out my AI art pages: https://linktr.ee/mooncryptowow

meta.prompt: an award winning xryhd mshn painting of a beautiful woman, complex robot, biomechanical,  insanely detailed, extremely fine details, very intricate, Extremely sharp focus, (photo realistic:1.65), cinematic lighting, art by h.r. giger and greg rutkowski , featured on zbrush central   <lora:xryhd:0.8>  <lora:mshn:0.3>
